<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.5">
<l>aḻuvaṉ ṟoḻuva ṉāṭik kāṇpaṉ pāṭi yalaṟṟuvaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaḻuval viṉaiyāl pakka nōkki nāṇik kaviḻntiruppaṉ</l>
<l>ceḻuvoṇ paḻaṉak kuṭantaik kiṭantāy centā maraikkaṇṇā</l>
<l>toḻuva ṉēṉai yuṉṟāḷ cērum vakaiyē cūḻkaṇṭāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dancing, I cry, I worship, singing in order to see [you] I babble.</l>
<l>Looking aside because of my pervasive harsh karma, I am ashamed [and] bent over.</l>
<l>You who lie in Kuṭantai with lush bright paddy fields, Kṛṣṇa with red lotus eyes,</l>
<l>see, think of a manner for me who worships [you] to join your feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
